  "prompt": "Are there pens with thick grip and thinner tip?  Is it available in India below 50 rupees?",
  "response": "Yes, pens with a thick grip and a thinner tip are available in India, often designed for comfort and precision while writing. Some brands offer affordable options that cater to such requirements. For example, you might find pens like the Linc Ocean Gel Pen or similar products within the price range of 50 rupees or below. These pens typically have a comfortable grip and provide smooth, fine writing.\n\nYou can check local stationery stores or online platforms like Amazon India, Flipkart, or local vendors like Office Linc, Pen Sanitizer for more options and deals. Be sure to check product reviews and descriptions to ensure they meet your specific needs.",
